{"word":"G3346 - μετατίθημι - metatíthēmi - met-at-ith'-ay-mee - Carry over","slug":"G3346","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μετατίθημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>metatíthēmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>met-at-ith'-ay-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Carry over"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B8;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - metatithe&#x0304;mi</b> - <i>met-at-ith'-ay-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3326\">G3326</a> and <a href=\"#/G5087\">G5087</a>; to <i>transfer</i>, that is, (literally) <i>transport</i>, (by implication) <i>exchange</i>, (reflexively) <i>change sides</i>, or (figuratively) <i>pervert:</i> - carry over, change, remove, translate, turn."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G114\">G114</a>, <a href=\"#/G115\">G115</a>, <a href=\"#/G1936\">G1936</a>, <a href=\"#/G2007\">G2007</a>, <a href=\"#/G3331\">G3331</a>, <a href=\"#/G3866\">G3866</a>, <a href=\"#/G3908\">G3908</a>, <a href=\"#/G4286\">G4286</a>, <a href=\"#/G4369\">G4369</a>, <a href=\"#/G4388\">G4388</a>, <a href=\"#/G5087\">G5087</a>"}]}